HSQLDatabaseConnection - Class in uncc
Simple wrapper class intended to provide high-level access to HyperSQL's Java connector specifically for the database schema utilized in this project.

HSQLDatabaseObject - Class in uncc.objects
Abstract base class used to enforce object standards across Java objects that will be used to create tables in our database.
HSQLDatabaseObject() - Constructor for class uncc.objects.HSQLDatabaseObject
 
HSQLDatabaseTable<E extends HSQLDatabaseObject> - Class in uncc.tables
Generalized parameterized abstract class used to automatically generate SQL insert, update, delete, findByID, getAll, and create queries and associated Java method handles for use by the user.
